des:
Prove yourself a die hard Disney fan with this Easy version of Disney Fan Quiz game.

Disney Fan Quiz Easy is an unofficial Disney trivia game. Alexa will ask you 5 multiple choice trivia questions about Disney movies and facts. You score points when you give correct answers. Just say "Alexa, start Disney Fan Quiz Easy" and have fun! 

Note: This game is not developed or sponsored by Disney. The developer is not an affiliate of Disney.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
